(921, 1, '2015-12-16 17:37:16', '2015-12-16 17:37:16', '<div class="body-journal">\r\n<div class="journal-content">\r\n<p class="journal-inner"><span class="drop-cap">I</span>t comes in at least once a year. The token NYC blizzard.\r\nBut last night we saw the opportunity to have a little fun. So we took our Burton snowboards and did what we could with the small slopes of Riverside Park.</p>\r\n<p class="journal-inner">It was eery to see the city without a single car out. Total silence everywhere. It was almost therapeutic. We walked down the west side highway in total solitude. Good times.\r\nMake the most out of every night.\r\n– Sebastian.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'NYC: LIGHTS OUT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-16 17:37:16', '2015-12-16 17:37:16', '', 18, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
