(418, 158, '2015-11-18 17:29:28', '2015-11-18 17:29:28', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-740" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-013.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+013" width="2000" height="1334" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="medium body-copy">\r\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left">\r\n<h2>MR. ROSS PINO &amp; HIS MANY BIKES</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span class="drop-cap">M</span>r. Ross Pino is by far and away the real deal. As a model/actor he''s constantly used in photoshoots by brands who are looking to buy his look/story. He''s one of those men out there who is far from being a faker, and so, is why we are sharing his long journeyed story on our featured storytellers section.\r\n\r\nThe pictures were taken by photographer @GlenAllsop\r\n\r\n<strong>We know how much love you have for riding. As not only an actor/model but also a father, is there a time limit as to when you''ll stop riding?</strong>\r\n\r\nI don''t think I''ll ever stop riding. I''ve had 5 bikes and I''ve built every single one of them. It does get harder to find the time with the different loves I have in my life now but for me it''s therapy, so I don''t see it going anywhere.\r\n\r\n<strong>What''s your favorite thing about older bikes vs newer production bikes?</strong>\r\n\r\nThere''s something inherently beautiful about a carburator. Its imperfection and inexactitude give the bike a soul.\r\n\r\n<strong>What''s the one thing you can''t ride without?</strong>\r\n\r\nI think eye protection is extremely important when riding. A helmet will save you from an accident but a good pair of shades will save you from getting <em>into</em> one... water, bugs, sun glare. I''ve never had a pair of frames which I''ve felt more comfortable driving in than the TATANO. They''ll never fly off my face.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-737" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-010.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+010" width="2000" height="1333" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-742" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Unknown-2400x1600.jpeg" alt="Unknown" width="2400" height="1600" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-738" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-011.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+011" width="2000" height="1333" /></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/product/tatano/">Explore the TATANO frame</a></span><img class="aligncenter wp-image-442 size-full" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/TATANO_FRONT.jpg" alt="TATANO_FRONT" width="2400" height="2000" /></p>', 'DUST', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'im-not-a-suit', '', '', '2016-01-09 00:43:35', '2016-01-09 00:43:35', '', 0, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/?p=418', 0, 'post', '', 0),
