 off their own success, indulging in projects that, if it wasn’t for their proven money-making record, would never have seen the green light, let alone the light of day.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="medium body-copy" style="margin: 0px 139.984375px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: WhitneyLight, WhitneyBook Times, serif; line-height: inherit; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 679.984375px; float: left; color: #2b2b2b; letter-spacing: 0.23999999463558197px;">\r\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0em 0px 1.76471em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: 1.76471em; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: baseline;">Such was the case surrounding the notoriously troubled production of <em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #2b2b2b; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0067334/" target="_blank">Le Mans</a></em>, a 1971 racing movie that starred, and was produced by, the late, great <a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #2b2b2b; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://www.mrporter.com/stylehelp/icons#stevemc">Mr Steve McQueen</a>. Based around the legendary 24-hour endurance motorsport race of the same name, <em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Le Mans</em> was the very definition of a passion project for 