(864, 161, '2015-12-15 00:50:02', '2015-12-15 00:50:02', '<div class="body-journal">\r\n<div class="journal-content">\r\n<p class="journal-inner"><span class="drop-cap">I</span>t comes in at least once a year. The token NYC blizzard.<br> But last night we saw the opportunity to have a little fun. So we took our Burton snowboards and&nbsp;did what we could with the small slopes of Riverside Park.</p>\r\n<p class="journal-inner">It was eery to see the city without a single car out. Total silence everywhere. It was almost therapeutic. We walked down the west side highway in total solitude. Good times.<br> Make the most out of every night.<br> – Sebastian.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'FROZEN IN TIME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-15 00:50:02', '2015-12-15 00:50:02', '', 10, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
